      <title>印度两省开始计票，莫迪支持率面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度周二开始在两个北部省份计票，出口民调预测，由于选民担心就业和收入问题，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在这两个省的选票将落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯签署法律吸引国防公司落户菲律宾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/marcos-signs-law-to-attract-defense-companies-to-philippines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯周二签署了一项法律，旨在吸引外国武器制造商在这个东南亚国家设厂，以发展本土国防工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/marcos-signs-law-to-attract-defense-companies-to-philippines</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:11:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称她稍后将考虑乌克兰加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯拒绝透露当选后是否会支持乌克兰加入北约，但她发誓，她将坚持让基辅领导人参与美国与弗拉基米尔·普京就结束持续冲突进行的任何谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中情局局长称误解可能加剧以色列与伊朗的冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/cia-chief-says-misunderstandings-could-worsen-israel-iran-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯警告说，错误的判断可能会阻碍未来几周缓和伊朗和以色列之间日益紧张的关系的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/cia-chief-says-misunderstandings-could-worsen-israel-iran-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家敦促英国征收“离境税”以防止富人离境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/economists-urge-uk-exit-tax-to-prevent-departures-of-wealthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高级经济学家和智囊团敦促财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 对富人征收“离境税”，每年征收高达 5 亿英镑（6.5 亿美元）的税款，以阻止富人离境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/economists-urge-uk-exit-tax-to-prevent-departures-of-wealthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥最高法院将审查 AMLO 的司法改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/mexico-s-supreme-court-will-review-amlo-s-judicial-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，墨西哥最高法院同意审查国会上个月通过的司法改革法案，批评人士认为该法案威胁到了该机构的独立性。这是上诉这项有争议的法案的最后手段，该法案要求法官由民众选举产生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/mexico-s-supreme-court-will-review-amlo-s-judicial-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称特朗普和德桑蒂斯利用飓风玩弄政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-accuses-trump-desantis-of-political-games-with-storms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯批评她的对手唐纳德·特朗普和另一位共和党人佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯在飓风海琳的恢复和飓风米尔顿的准备工作中“玩弄政治花招”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-accuses-trump-desantis-of-political-games-with-storms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚执政联盟选举前岌岌可危</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/romanian-ruling-coalition-teeters-on-the-brink-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在罗马尼亚一系列选举前不到两个月，罗马尼亚的执政联盟濒临崩溃，原因是一个小党派采取行动抗议最高法院做出的一项有争议的裁决，将一名极右翼候选人排除在总统竞选之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/romanian-ruling-coalition-teeters-on-the-brink-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lululemon 创始人价值 6000 万美元的房子因选举标志被毁坏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁 Lululemon Athletica Inc. 创始人奇普·威尔逊 (Chip Wilson) 价值 6000 万美元的豪宅变成了涂满涂鸦的导火索，象征着加拿大省级选举的两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的税收计划因竞选承诺遭遇现实而受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当英国首相凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 和财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 策划工党在英国的执政之路时，他们希望通过提高私募股权和超级富豪“非本地”居民的税收来为关键支出计划提供资金。现在，这些承诺正在变成现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
